        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nExclusions are part of the fix, for some reason there are two OSGi frameworks on the classpath, and mocking framework fails in setup phase. It's hard to judge what caused this dependency hazard, as I'm not the owner of original changes. However as you can see it's exactly how the build failed again after your proposal to not include my exclusions for eclipse SDK test dependency.",
